Package: jujutsu
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Git-compatible VCS that is both simple and powerful
 Jujutsu (jj) is a Git-compatible distributed version control system.
 It provides an alternative user interface and workflow on top of Git
 repositories, with features like automatic rebase, first-class conflicts,
 and a full operation log with undo support.
